name: The Munchies Free Illustrations
description:
Illustrations for all the foodie lovers out there! Get pizza, taco, sushi, cake, salad, or anything you want!


All the illustrations in this project were made with Blush, which means that you can customize them however you want!


It works like building blocks made of vector arms, legs, and emotions. Mix elements to create different characters and scenes.


Install the Blush plugin so you can customize everything.
